</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The given type, <ref refid="group__sensing__sensor__types_1ga9f6bc03e84167bf0b1ae8ea4fe016223" kindref="member">SENSING_SENSOR_TYPE_ALL</ref> to get reporters with all types. </para>
