</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>max_handles</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The max count of the <computeroutput>reporter_handles</computeroutput> array input. Can get real count number via <ref refid="group__sensing__sensor_1ga2c5cfb298b2dfde967edfdd987115021" kindref="member">sensing_sensor_get_reporters_count</ref> </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>reporter_handles</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Input handles array for receiving found reporter sensor instances </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>number of reporters found, 0 returned if not found. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
